sequenceDiagram
    participant iOS as iOS App<br/>EventSource
    participant Vapor as Vapor Backend<br/>SSE Handler
    participant Python as sdk-wrapper.py<br/>async iterator
    participant CLI as Claude CLI<br/>OAuth Session
    participant API as Anthropic API

    iOS->>Vapor: POST /api/v1/chat/stream<br/>{"prompt": "Say hi"}
    activate Vapor
    Vapor->>Python: Process spawn<br/>python3 sdk-wrapper.py "Say hi"
    activate Python
    Python->>CLI: query(prompt, include_partial_messages=True)
    activate CLI
    CLI->>API: HTTP POST /v1/messages<br/>Authorization: Bearer [oauth_token]
    activate API

    Note over API: Model generates tokens

    API-->>CLI: {"type":"content_block_delta","delta":{"text":"Hello"}}
    CLI-->>Python: stdout: partial message JSON
    Python-->>Vapor: NDJSON: {"type":"message","content":"Hello"}
    Vapor-->>iOS: SSE: data: {"type":"message","content":"Hello"}

    API-->>CLI: {"type":"content_block_delta","delta":{"text":"! How"}}
    CLI-->>Python: stdout: partial message JSON
    Python-->>Vapor: NDJSON: {"type":"message","content":"Hello! How"}
    Vapor-->>iOS: SSE: data: {"type":"message","content":"Hello! How"}

    API-->>CLI: {"type":"content_block_delta","delta":{"text":" can I help?"}}
    CLI-->>Python: stdout: partial message JSON
    Python-->>Vapor: NDJSON: {"type":"message","content":"Hello! How can I help?"}
    Vapor-->>iOS: SSE: data: {"type":"message","content":"Hello! How can I help?"}

    API-->>CLI: {"type":"message_stop"}
    deactivate API
    CLI-->>Python: stdout: final message + cost
    deactivate CLI
    Python-->>Vapor: NDJSON: {"type":"done","cost":0.0419}
    deactivate Python
    Vapor-->>iOS: SSE: data: {"type":"done","cost":0.0419}
    deactivate Vapor

    Note over iOS: Display complete message<br/>Show cost: $0.04
